<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Hyperlink Example</title>
</head>
<body>

<h2>Working of Hyperlinks in HTML</h2>

<p>
    1. Open Google in the same tab:
    <a href="https://www.google.com">Visit Google</a>
</p>

<p>
    2. Open YouTube in a new tab:
    <a href="https://www.youtube.com" target="_blank">Visit YouTube</a>
</p>

<p>
    4. Link to another page (example: about.html):
    <a href="about.html">Go to About Page</a>
</p>

</body>
</html>